sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Agent A
    participant ES as extractMemories
    participant SD as Storage
    participant NE as Agent B<br/>（新会话）
    participant MD as Memory<br/>Discovery
    A->>ES: 会话结束，提取记忆
    ES->>SD: 保存到 .claude/teams/
    SD->>MD: Agent B 开始新会话
    MD->>MD: 语义搜索
    MD->>NE: 注入相关记忆
    NE->>NE: 结合新知识和历史洞察
